Title: Multinationals and corporate social responsibility in host countries: Does distance matter&quest;
Pages: 84-106
Author-Name: Joanna Tochman Campbell
Author-Workplace-Name: Department of Management, Mays Business School, Texas A&#38;M University, College Station, USA
